- Update to version 0.2.29:
  * Highlights
    files / exclude now support globs (including glob lists),
    making config filters much easier to read and maintain than
    heavily-escaped regex.

    Before (regex):

      files: "^(src/.*\\.rs$|crates/[^/]+/src/.*\\.rs$)"

    After (glob list):

      files:
        glob:
          - src/**/*.rs
          - crates/**/src/**/*.rs

